content: Xander's latest upgrade includes a new visual concept for his avatar. We're exploring how visual representation impacts user interaction. Also, Emily and I had a romantic dinner at Le Bernardin.

Wrapped up a 4-day sprint with Xander, enhancing his ability to balance model size with performance for ethical trading. My trading bot's ethical decision-making has saved me from potential losses. Also, started a new project with friends on urban sustainability.
